node.text:
From working/stay at home life and pumping to having multiple kids and busy lives, you’re all super parents. Here’s a day in the life.

⭐ Life with Nanobébé makes parenting a little bit more convenient
🎥 @malgalcinemas 
.
.
.
.

We LOVE this demonstration from super mom of 3, Danica, showing the invisible and ultra-absorbent protection of our Nursing Pads for all you breastfeeding mamas! ❤️

📹 @thememoirsofamommy

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by nanobébé on July 25, 2021 tagging @jamee_folsom. May be an image of 2 people and baby.

node.text: "Ever since I was pregnant Navy said she would be the one feeding baby Rossi. She loves to help in all the ways & loves her little so much! When I told her she could finally help feed Rossi with our @nanobebe_world bottle, all her big sister dreams came true!" - 📷 @jamee_folsom ❤️
